reviewtext: Durability: I haven't really put them up to the durability test yet as i've only had them for 2 weeks.Sound: Above average for a cheap headphone. I can only compare them to my Fata1ity USB PC Headset and my Sony MDR-V6 cans which both produce much better sound but cost way more money.Comfort: Comfortable, I might just be forever sold on over-the-ear vs in-ear headphones because of these. They are light and I forget that i'm wearing them.
